Application of cerebral function imaging in research on the acupoints specificity. To explore the effect of cerebral function imaging in research on the acupoints specificity. Relevant literatures are retrieved and their results are compared. The results reveals as the follows: (1) Acupuncture can ameliorate cerebral blood flow hypoperfusion in patients with cerebrovascular disease, which maybe one of the mechanisms of acupuncture effect (2) Acupuncture treatment has selectivity regulation role, which is related to the state of body and brain